@laanwj I forgot to disable the OSX builder for the initial merge. Disabled now and it's all green.

See the note here: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/4749/files#diff-7dcfe27d5e2ccfc80ea9b88dd14ada7dR34
The OSX SDK url needs to be hidden, since it's not distributable. We can create that encrypted string as a next step, then hook OSX back up.
